title: Raw ideas have an expiration
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Ideas or notes that are left unprocessed will eventually expire because we may forget what they remind us of or the context behind them. To avoid this, we [[aim to write ACID notes|Aim to write ACID notes]] by expanding raw ideas into self-contained thoughts within a day or two.